{"tid":1256143,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"行動者們，別以為Telegram比較安全","createTime":"2019-06-25T00:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T09:08:37.000Z","uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd098b994b6d77910a705d1f3591b13aff881147","tid":1256143,"uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"Telegram保密仲差過whatsapp, 最好係Signal<br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp: 所有對話有加密，只有對話雙方睇到，但最衰係由Facebook營運<br />\n<br />\nTelegram: 正常對話無加密，只係Secret chat有加密。Telegram最大優點係Group人數無限, 但保安唔得<br />\n<br />\nSignal : 所有信息加密，而且係開源軟件，開放比全世界監察有無後門程式，無由任何公司營運， 斯諾登都係用佢來逃避FBI追蹤， 美國政界，國會議員，總統都用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1043826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1043826&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443mt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=01865c06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1043826&h=55e26ea8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1043826</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzS8wh3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzS8wh3.png&h=b1f004dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdc963d60aa412c51effdfa6770bdea8a82df5d6","tid":1256143,"uid":5591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:49:26.000Z","msg":"開頭話whatsapp,呢樣唔得個樣唔得水人過TG,千辛萬苦開荒到TG開始多人用，而家又話TG唔得&hellip;"},{"pid":"919330ba3ab58750dff3a513f4ea37a87ea0b9be","tid":1256143,"uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdc963d60aa412c51effdfa6770bdea8a82df5d6","tid":1256143,"uid":5591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T01:49:26.000Z","msg":"開頭話whatsapp,呢樣唔得個樣唔得水人過TG,千辛萬苦開荒到TG開始多人用，而家又話TG唔得&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"TG一向都係無保密，啲人最初見佢有secret chat同閱後即焚，就吹話好勁"}]}